reviewText:
ROY ROGERS WASN'T THE KING OF THE COWBOYS FOR NOTHIN THIS  SET OF HIS MOVIES COVER THE EARLY
PERIOD ACTION OATERS THE MIDDLE FULL BLOWN MUSIC WESTERNS AND THE MORE VIOLENT COLOUR WESTERNS
A GREAT SELECTION OF HIS MOVIES.I WOULD HAVE GIVEN IT 5 STARS BUT ONE OF THE MOVIES IS POOR QUALITY.
ALAN
Love the old cowboys and all the  sidekicks they have with them.  tv today could use some tips from these old shows
